		<abstract>
			<para>This Developer Guide is intended for software developers who
				want to use the Rackspace Cloud Identity Service v2.0
				API for  identity management and authentication to
				Rackspace Cloud Services.  Developers will learn how
				to use the v2.0 API for authentication, identity
				administration, and access control of </para>
